                           <desc>- The scribe used compressed script to accommodate the end of the text: fols 79vb-83ra. - Omitted letters or words inserted interlineally: e.g., fols. 4rb, 13va, 21va, 45rb, 57rb, 67va, 73ra, 81vb. - Omitted letter added at the beginning of the line in small script, possibly in a secondary hand: <locus target="#26rb">fol.  26rb</locus>. - Erasures: fols. 12va, 17ra, 72rb. - Erasures marked with red lines: <locus target="#12ra">fol.  12ra</locus>. - Correction written over erasure in red ink in the main hand: <locus target="#42rb">fol.  42rb</locus>. - Immediate corrections indicated by lines over the word: fols. 27vb, 62va, 80rb (here in a secondary hand). - Immediate corrections indicated by thin black or red dashes above and below the letters: e.g., fols. 32rb, 36ra, 55vb, 72vb. - Lacunae (spaces for rubricated names left unfilled): e.g., fols. 40vb, 66va, 68ra, 72rb. - Scribbles and doodles: e.g., fols. 1r, 2v, 15r, 60r, 83r, 84r.</desc>
